title: Decades-old murders in South Florida attributed to Brazilian serial killer
author: WPLG Local 10
comment: Another episode of the Da Florida Horror Show 💀😳 2021 continues....
Seeing the husband of one of the women really got to me..
Vengeance belongs to God and He will repay.
description: Roberto Wagner Fernandes, the man now connected to these killings, died in a 2005 plane crash, say the investigators who cracked the cold cases.
